At Luxury Gardens, we specialise in award-winning luxury garden design, creating breathtaking outdoor spaces for over twenty years. Working across London, Surrey, Sussex, and Kent, we design and build everything from stunning, entertaining gardens to Mediterranean courtyards, Victorian hideaways, and sprawling country gardens.

Luxury Garden Design Philosophy

Our award-winning garden designers and landscape architects take a highly personalised and creative approach to every project, ensuring that each luxury garden design is original and deeply reflective of your lifestyle.

â€‹

With each design project, we present two distinct design concepts, allowing you to explore different visions and styles for your garden.


You may choose to proceed with a single concept or blend elements from both, resulting in a refined, tailor-made luxury garden design that feels effortlessly in tune with your home and lifestyle.

Luxury Landscaping & Build

Our luxury garden landscaping service guarantees that the design transitions into a project executed with meticulous attention to detail, care, and outstanding craftsmanship.

 

We use the highest-quality landscaping and surface materials and industry-leading construction techniques to bring your garden to life, creating an outdoor space that unites design, style, structure, and longevity.

 

We manage every detail of the garden build process from the design to the final element, ensuring your investment is carefully managed and the finished garden reflects the vision, quality, and standards you expect.
